Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.14,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:36.97,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:04.86,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.00,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:22.35,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:27.08,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:34.02,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Shinobu's divorce is official.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, big headlines, and a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, you can have this... take a look at it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway it's the end, for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But knowing you, you might choose your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a difficult decision: take the money, or dump your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,28. The Christmas Candles
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Shinobu residence...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Mariko did what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How badly was Misaki-san hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We sent her to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We are fortunate that only her arm was injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...and with treatment it should not be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's the first such incident in the school's history,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...and we are very deeply concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly, terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get there right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Mariko is not at the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She left the classroom after the incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that she's not home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I shouldn't ask... but what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood spurted up to the ceiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They say she always carries a knife in her bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Her father had 3 lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The classroom was an ocean of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The school was in an uproar over Mariko-san's incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that girl is a Sorority member!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What! You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to call her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll... go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She may not have gotten home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where can Mariko have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Obasama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The vice-principal called, and I was just now speaking to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why Mariko would do such a thing to that other girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Our family situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that it caused you problems too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what did the vice-principal say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She's suspended until the school board decides what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspended? I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's okay... we'll stop by after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'm going to the hospital now to see Misaki-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...and then I'll be going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I see Mariko-san, I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Takada Hospital, in Kyozaki City, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...in the afternoon Misaki-san returned from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I felt a sense of relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was obvious that her injury wasn't that serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll check several places for her and then stop at your place later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where shall we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Around the station I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok! Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, ease up! It's right in front of me now and I'm working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is that you, Hisako?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alone, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I need to talk to you a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I have a deadline today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Mariko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mariko" ...she said?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to prepare tea for ten. Can you lend a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But... today isn't scheduled as a Sorority...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an unscheduled meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is only for senior Sorority members.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This concerns the case of Shinobu Mariko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She has brought disgrace upon the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to consider an appropriate punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Miya-sama is deeply concerned as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am really sorry, I have a commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please ask another member for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been suspended until the board meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you think she'll be punished?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The rumors say 2 or 3 months suspension...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the daughter of a celebrity who gave the school an endowment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So the school will want to be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't give me that nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold the meeting and expel her now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you all be quiet? My wound is hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt really bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've been waiting for you to call back all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to disturb your work but,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...but something awful happened concerning Mariko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry... your husband just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...Mariko!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko! It must be Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:11:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hisako! What happened... to Mariko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear! Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I'd do if my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike yours, mine aren't really that close, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, I'm wondering,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...how is she feeling, alone and crying somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mariko-san, who is helpless to do anything about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Loving both her parents, she doesn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...just because it is a matter of love between adults,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...we mustn't get involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,2 hotdogs and 2 cups of soup, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have some. You must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't eat stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, I'll eat both.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm! Not bad. It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the best, but it's warm, and good enough for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk with your mouth full, barbarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh... this mustard is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm not asking you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm asking your stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good. Your stomach is honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We zoomed around the freeway like crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...and climbed up the observatory at the harbor,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...so we could go to Chinatown, or the foreign cemeteries...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say where, and we'll go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She finally calmed down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, she wanted to drive, so we drove around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we went pretty far, but now we're back at the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a light snack, and now she's dozing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She insisted I not call anyone, so I sneaked out when she nodded off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, was the girl badly injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She's worried about that, and starts panicking when she thinks of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. I'll watch her a bit more, then bring her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, tell her family not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh good, both of you can relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinomiya-san is with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved and exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I am too... I'm... I'm very relieved. Thank you very much, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, it's lit. But, thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That night,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Mariko-san returned shortly after 8 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can stay here with you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! Please, I'd like that... Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. Let's play a card game before we go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But, first I have something to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's okay. Try not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to visit Misaki-san at her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't seriously hurt... it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,After abandoning my mother and I... Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business anymore what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I attack my classmates, or kill somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:16:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to be nice and pretend to be my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you scold me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you keep forgiving him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody is lying! This house is filled with lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact I was born is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My own existence right now, is a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I should just disappear! I want to disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I hate myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave Mariko-san alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is... what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they pretty? I've been collecting them since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,On birthdays or Christmas, I would fill the house with candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to spend time with my family and my holiday candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Papa was never here to share them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Over and over, never able to be with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But... today... he's finally here. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's today? What special day is today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:44.29,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The last day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What... are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather see it burned down! The whole house!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, Mariko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn everything down if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but listen to what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do... and whatever happens... never hate yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.01,0:18:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't treat yourself like dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Without resorting to boasting or arrogance,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...you can find the good within you and love it always.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I hate myself! I hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm selfish and irresponsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I hurt everyone around me, and no one cares about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It may seem to you that I'm a worthless man,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...and people who know me probably think I'm worthless,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...not taking care of my family, a job without prestige,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...and a life without any real direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I believe even I have some good inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe no one else notices it. I'm the only one that knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something for me to nurture and love in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you can't live without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, if you have only that much and nothing else, you can live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't love yourself, who will love you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:20:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't love yourself, whom will you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you can. Because I love you in spite of everything, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...what a wonderful Father, and loving Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and such an honest Mariko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each of them is such a great person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet, in spite of that, their family is being destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is that, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just too sad for me, and I can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As you all know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...yesterday a shameful incident disgraced our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night we convened an emergency meeting of the senior members.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, I'd like to make an announcement to all the members.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A decision was made unanimously by secret ballot,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...to expel Shinobu Mariko-san from the Sorority, effective yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please state your objections now, if any...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair! That's too severe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I don't know what got into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something inside forced me to jump up and start shouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too one-sided!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.76,0:22:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you listen to Shinobu-san's side of the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There must've been some reason for Shinobu-san to do what she did!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. That's a reasonable point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.69,0:22:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue, Misonoo-san. State your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But the decision is already made and it is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please understand this, and then state your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.71,0:22:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, the decision was based on the shameful facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The cause of her actions is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"Decision"? "Absolute"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of Sorority is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.34,0:22:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We are all students in the same school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,An "absolute decision"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Decisions can't be forced on one student by another like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What authority justifies such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.02,0:23:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.37,0:23:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has a right to state her opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on. Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I will leave the Sorority too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That... that is my "decision"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear Brother, I... I left the Sorority!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.51,0:24:13.71,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.71,0:24:19.18,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.65,0:24:24.79,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.79,0:24:30.26,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.00,0:24:36.54,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.54,0:24:42.01,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:44.74,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.74,0:24:47.55,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.55,0:24:49.95,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.95,0:24:55.22,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.08,0:25:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After Mariko's incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.13,0:25:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...Kaoru becomes convinced that the Sorority must be abolished.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.81,0:25:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When she confides to Saint-Juste her plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.86,0:25:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...Saint-Juste is shaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.21,0:25:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Each follow their own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.17,0:25:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The fated day of reckoning draws near.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.86,0:25:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: The Student Assembly
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.51,0:25:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
